title.rendered: STEDI 2 PACK T10 W5W WEDGE LED LIGHT 28MM

content.rendered:
STEDI T10 Wedge 12 SMD LED Light Conversion Kit with a height of 28mm often used for parkers, licence plate & interior application.

DETAILS

You’ve upgraded your headlights to LED now your looking at your parkers in all their awful amber glory. Our T10 wedge LED are the finishing touch to bring the front end of your car back in to the 20th century.

Also known as: W5W / 194 / 501 / W16W / 921

KEY TECHNICAL FEATURES | T10

  • CANBUS friendly – Error free operation
  • Not Polarity Sensitive – our T10’s wont fail if you plug them in the wrong way.
  • Constant Current circuit – Avoids compromising LED life & provides consistent illumination across all LEDs
  • Compatible from 9v to 30v circuits.
  • 12SMD LED for uniform light distribution

COMMON USES FOR T10 GLOBES

  • Interior Dome Lights
  • Interior Map Lights
  • Parker Lights
  • License Plate Lights
  • Boot Light

Sold in packs of 2

SPECIFICATIONS

HOUSING MATERIAL Aluminium
LED 3030
LUMINOUS FLUX 239 Lumens
POWER 0.2a @ 13.6v
COMPATIBLE VOLTAGE DC 12v and 24v
LIFESPAN 30,000 Hours
CANBUS Compatible
CONNECTOR TYPE T10
INGRESS PROTECTION IP65
OPERATING TEMP -40°c to + 80°c
CERTIFICATION CE, ROHS
RENDERING INDEX 83 CRI

 

 

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • 2 x STEDI T10 W5W Wedge LED Lights
